It's a magic mirror!

190
00:10:21,547 --> 00:10:25,147
If one side of it is dark, it looks like a mirror.

191
00:10:25,147 --> 00:10:29,247
But if you light up the dark side, it becomes like glass!

192
00:10:29,247 --> 00:10:31,347
